result.name: Tao Heung Training Restaurant

reviews.text: great Chinese dim sum with special design, some taste good but some are not. As they say, this restaurant is for testing new dishes, so you decide if it's great or not. overall, it's pretty good, but it's just too far

Nice dim sum restaurants where I believe most of the chefs are in training (from the name). Some of their dim sum dishes like the rich noodle rolls are actually very good, but I find the Ha Gao (Shrimp rolls)'s skin to be kind of thick. Besides that I do believe they use very high quality tea.
Consistently good dim sum, imaginative presentation. Minion sha bao very funny and tasty, also crab meat "macaron" . Dinner menu is also very good.
The best price restuarant in Hong Kong. Even there is a training restaurant,  food quality and service both are excellent.
The foods so delicious and the place is nice

result.name: 稻香訓練酒樓

reviews.text: great Chinese dim sum with special design, some taste good but some are not. As they say, this restaurant is for testing new dishes, so you decide if it's great or not. overall, it's pretty good, but it's just too far
今晚是端午節正日，去這裡食夜食。訂了8:15 12人，未食先要比入會費300玩！（唔知有甚麼優惠）。服務一般留單，菜單重複，好多菜式已售罄。20幾蚊支細的燕京！（都好貴） 冰鎮咕嚕肉和牛肉粒都唔錯。抄飯飯身都一粒粒幾光身GOOD，隻鵝就麻麻地， 正體相一般。（應該平日去食會好啲啩？？）
是一間頗寕靜的酒楼,点心款色特別多,味道好.如果是會員,還有其他優惠.
